Overview
--------
This directory contains the wikitles corpus, released for  the WMT series
of shared tasks. It consists of parallel wikipedia titles.

There is a subdirectory for each version.

The code used to extract the wikititles is available at https://github.com/bhaddow/wikipedia-interlanguage-titles

